data.description: Great home located just minutes from Navarre Beach! As you walk thru the front door you are welcomed to this perfectly laid out 3/2 split floor plan with just under 1300sqft. This home is a clean, open slate and ready for your personal touch! You will love the wood laminate flooring throughout the kitchen, living & bedrooms and the tile flooring in the bathrooms. The side entry garage with long driveway provides you with plenty of room for all of your vehicles not to mention the spacious backyard begging for your touch! All of this and at a price that cannot be beat! Don't miss out on your chance to have the perfect starter home, retirement home, or investment property right here in Navarre!
